ActSafe Streets and Communities Act
SubjectOrder Fixing May 3, 2012 as the Day on which Certain Sections of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing May 3, 2012 as the day on which sections 135 and 136 of the SAFE STREETS AND COMMUNITIES ACT, chapter 1 of the Statutes of Canada 2012, COME INTO FORCE. These sections amend the International Transfer of Offenders Act.
